# JITO JEAP - Comprehensive Approval Workflow System

## Overview

This document describes the redesigned approval workflow system that provides clear, easy-to-understand status management for admins. The system tracks applications through 4 approval levels with per-form status tracking.

---

## 1. WORKFLOW ARCHITECTURE

### 1.1 Approval Levels (Sequential)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    USER SUBMITS APPLICATION                     │
│                    (All 7 forms submitted)                      │
└────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                             ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      APEX REVIEW (Level 1)                      │
│  - Review all 7 forms individually                              │
│  - Can approve, reject, or hold each form                       │
│  - All forms must be approved to proceed                        │
│  - Status: apex_status (pending/approved/rejected/on_hold)      │
└────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                             ↓
                    (All forms approved?)
                             ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              WORKING COMMITTEE REVIEW (Level 2)                 │
│  - Review all 7 forms individually                              │
│  - Can approve, reject, or hold each form                       │
��  - All forms must be approved to proceed                        │
│  - Status: working_committee_status                             │
└────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                             ↓
                    (All forms approved?)
                             ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   CHAPTER REVIEW (Level 3)                      │
│  - Review all 7 forms individually                              │
│  - Can approve, reject, or hold each form                       │
│  - All forms must be approved to proceed                        │
│  - Status: chapter_status                                       │
└────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                             ↓
                    (All forms approved?)
                             ↓
┌─────────────��───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  APEX FINAL REVIEW (Level 4)                    │
│  - Final review by Apex                                         │
│  - Can approve, reject, or hold each form                       │
│  - All forms must be approved to complete                       │
│  - Status: apex_final_status                                    │
└────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘
                             ↓
                    (All forms approved?)
                             ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    APPLICATION COMPLETED                        │
│                  (application_status = 'approved')              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


```
